Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: In The Olden Time: Before 11 September
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sx6kb
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 19 Oct 2001
Alistair Cooke reflects on how the September 11th attack has changed the American psyche, and considers how letters filled with anthrax are exacerbating the problems.